
What is Amazon QuickSight?

Business Intelligence (BI) service in AWS.

Lets you create interactive dashboards, visualizations, and reports from your data.

Fully managed, serverless, and scalable.



---

Key Features

Data sources → connects to Redshift, RDS, DynamoDB, S3, Athena, EMR, and more.

Interactive dashboards → charts, graphs, heatmaps, maps.

SPICE engine → Super-fast in-memory calculation engine for quick analytics.

Collaboration → share dashboards with other users securely.

ML insights → auto-detect anomalies and trends using built-in machine learning.

Pay-per-session or subscription → cost-effective for scaling users.